339
00:18:44,832 --> 00:18:45,791
<font face="Serif" size="18">No!</font>

340
00:18:46,792 --> 00:18:48,377
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, sticks-to-walls guy,</font>

341
00:18:48,461 --> 00:18:50,546
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess we were both wrong.</font>

342
00:18:51,756 --> 00:18:53,007
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, God.</font>

343
00:18:57,678 --> 00:18:59,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [grunting]
- [screaming]</font>

344
00:19:01,265 --> 00:19:02,933
<font face="Serif" size="18">Rick! Please!</font>

345
00:19:03,017 --> 00:19:04,310
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jerry, I've got the creature.</font>

346
00:19:04,393 --> 00:19:06,354
<font face="Serif" size="18">I knew it. I knew it.</font>

347
00:19:06,437 --> 00:19:07,855
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goddamn it!</font>

348
00:19:08,814 --> 00:19:09,940
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screaming]</font>

349
00:19:13,903 --> 00:19:15,071
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, God!</font>

350
00:19:17,073 --> 00:19:18,074
<font face="Serif" size="18">Goddamn it.</font>

351
00:19:25,831 --> 00:19:27,458
<font face="Serif" size="18">Holy shit, that was close.</font>

352
00:19:27,541 --> 00:19:28,542
<font face="Serif" size="18">Close to what?</font>

353
00:19:28,626 --> 00:19:32,046
<font face="Serif" size="18">Close to everyone but your son
getting anything they want forever.</font>

354
00:19:32,129 --> 00:19:33,172
<font face="Serif" size="18">You saved me.</font>

355
00:19:33,255 --> 00:19:35,424
<font face="Serif" size="18">I will never stop holding this over you,</font>

356
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:37,134
<font face="Serif" size="18">as if that buys me anything.</font>

357
00:19:37,218 --> 00:19:39,637
<font face="Serif" size="18">- We should get you some clothes, son.
- Oh, oh!</font>

358
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,138
<font face="Serif" size="18">[upbeat music playing]</font>

359
00:19:44,308 --> 00:19:46,143
<font face="Serif" size="18">I can just feel the savings.</font>

360
00:19:47,812 --> 00:19:49,271
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey, wait, uh...</font>

361
00:19:49,355 --> 00:19:52,024
<font face="Serif" size="18">Got this at the crazy place we just were.</font>

362
00:19:52,108 --> 00:19:55,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">It may look like someone stuck
a hand-written fortune in there last second,</font>

363
00:19:55,528 --> 00:19:57,822
<font face="Serif" size="18">but I'm pretty sure that's just the way it came.</font>

364
00:19:57,905 --> 00:20:00,116
<font face="Serif" size="18">Besides, these don't mean anything.</font>

365
00:20:01,409 --> 00:20:03,494
<font face="Serif" size="18">Jerry, while I appreciate the sentiment,</font>

366
00:20:03,577 --> 00:20:06,288
<font face="Serif" size="18">this is a huge waste of the last real fortune.</font>

367
00:20:06,372 --> 00:20:08,040
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh. I'm sorry. I just...</font>

368
00:20:08,124 --> 00:20:09,625
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's cool, it's cool.</font>

369
00:20:09,709 --> 00:20:11,502
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Thanks, friend.
- Friend?</font>

370
00:20:11,585 --> 00:20:12,920
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Did you just say friend?
- What?</font>

371
00:20:13,003 --> 00:20:15,339
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What did I do?
- You fucking idiot! I'm not your friend!</font>

372
00:20:15,423 --> 00:20:16,966
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why did you think I was your friend?</font>

373
00:20:17,049 --> 00:20:18,426
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look at this, you piece of shit.</font>

374
00:20:18,509 --> 00:20:20,344
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yeah, yeah, yeah, so?
- I was immortal!</font>

375
00:20:20,428 --> 00:20:22,054
<font face="Serif" size="18">I was immortal for that whole fight.</font>

376
00:20:22,138 --> 00:20:24,014
<font face="Serif" size="18">All I had to do was never make a new friend.</font>

377
00:20:24,098 --> 00:20:26,684
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Jesus fucking Christ, Jerry.
- I'm sorry! We're not friends!</font>

378
00:20:26,767 --> 00:20:28,018
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah, too late, bonehead.</font>

379
00:20:28,102 --> 00:20:29,937
<font face="Serif" size="18">It doesn't say "new permanent friend."</font>

380
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:32,815
<font face="Serif" size="18">All friendships end, especially new ones.</font>

381
00:20:32,898 --> 00:20:36,402
<font face="Serif" size="18">Well, maybe that's a fate
the two of us still control.</font>

382
00:20:38,904 --> 00:20:39,989
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sobbing]</font>

383
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:43,826
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm sorry I did that.</font>

384
00:20:43,909 --> 00:20:44,869
<font face="Serif" size="18">It's fine.</font>

385
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:48,289
<font face="Serif" size="18">["Theme from <i>Taxi"</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18"> playing]</font>

386
00:21:26,243 --> 00:21:28,746
<font face="Serif" size="18">[announcer] <i>The zoo. Animals.
Balloons. Moats. Cages.</i></font>

387
00:21:28,829 --> 00:21:30,331
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>A fun time for the whole family.</i></font>

388
00:21:30,414 --> 00:21:32,416
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>But you don't care about that. You're a zebra.</i></font>

389
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:34,752
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>You're here for the unparalleled
dining experience</i></font>

390
00:21:34,835 --> 00:21:36,879
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>of hand-fed zebra food. Delicious.</i></font>

391
00:21:36,962 --> 00:21:38,798
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Hey, wait. Don't eat...</i></font>

392
00:21:38,881 --> 00:21:41,175
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>That's for the zebras. It's making you sick!</i></font>

393
00:21:41,258 --> 00:21:42,092
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>What are you doing?</i></font>

394
00:21:42,176 --> 00:21:45,137
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Why have they left the zebra-feeding
to the people who come to the zoo?</i></font>

395
00:21:45,221 --> 00:21:48,682
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Is that the only way the zebras can get food?
They're so hungry. What is happening?</i></font>

396
00:21:48,766 --> 00:21:50,184
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>We're out of zebra food. Okay?</i></font>

397
00:21:50,267 --> 00:21:52,228
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>There's no food left. Don't come to the zoo.</i></font>

398
00:21:52,311 --> 00:21:55,439
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>This was supposed to be a commercial for zebras,
targeted to zebras.</i></font>

399
00:21:55,523 --> 00:21:58,317
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>The premise itself was questionable, but this,
this is a nightmare!</i></font>

400
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,277
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Don't go to the zoo. Stay away from the zoo.</i></font>

401
00:22:00,361 --> 00:22:02,738
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>What are you doing in the booth?
Get out! Get out!</i></font>

402
00:22:02,822 --> 00:22:04,281
<font face="Serif" size="18">- <i>You're mad with--
</i></font><font face="Serif" size="18">- [gunshot]</font>

403
00:22:05,699 --> 00:22:08,118
<font face="Serif" size="18">[man] <i>Eat it. Eat zebra food.</i></font>

404
00:22:08,202 --> 00:22:10,830
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, I guess I can't blame Dad
for being confused</font>

405
00:22:10,913 --> 00:22:12,540
<font face="Serif" size="18">about what to do with the zebra food.</font>

406
00:22:12,623 --> 00:22:14,750
<font face="Serif" size="18">Also, I have no idea why they're running this ad,</font>

407
00:22:14,834 --> 00:22:16,919
<font face="Serif" size="18">like, on a loop? There were murders in it,</font>

408
00:22:17,002 --> 00:22:20,172
<font face="Serif" size="18">and it was specifically telling you
to do the thing it didn't want you to do</font>

409
00:22:20,256 --> 00:22:21,841
<font face="Serif" size="18">until the very end, when it reversed.</font>

410
00:22:21,924 --> 00:22:24,134
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why would they sell the zebra food
in the gift shop,</font>

411
00:22:24,218 --> 00:22:26,428
<font face="Serif" size="18">unless... I mean,
do the zebras shop in here?</font>

412
00:22:26,512 --> 00:22:28,013
<font face="Serif" size="18">Are we the ones in the zoo?</font>

413
00:22:28,097 --> 00:22:29,265
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, is that the twist?</font>

414
00:22:29,348 --> 00:22:31,183
<font face="Serif" size="18">Okay, we're-- It's a human zoo. Got it.</font>

